  </ul>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Proactive Brand Monitoring:</strong> Brands cannot afford to be passive. It is crucial to actively and regularly monitor how the brand, its products, and its key topics are being represented in AIOs and other LLMs. This involves routinely testing relevant prompts and search queries to audit the AI's output for accuracy and sentiment.</li>
